.DT
player_refreshed
Disk World creator help
player_refreshed

.SH Name
.SP 5 5
player_refreshed -  This function gets called by the player object whenever a player refreshes, or by any of the various objects that delete players when they get deleted.
.EP

.SH Syntax
.SI 5
varargs void player_refreshed(object player,
int totally)
.EI

.SH Defined in
.SI 5
/obj/handlers/refresh.c
.EI

.SH Description
.SP 5 5

This function gets called by the player object whenever
a player refreshes, or by any of the various objects that delete
players when they get deleted.  You should never call
this function directly.

.EP

